title: Google Safe Browsing
description: This connector enriches domain names and URLs with threat intelligence from Google Safe Browsing. Google Safe Browsing maintains a list of websites that might pose risks for malware, abusive extensions, phishing, malicious and intrusive ads, and social engineering attacks.
